In `module-why-choose-section.tsx`, the left-side image:

- **Default source:** `/images/atursondrIntro.webp` (constant `WHY_CHOOSE_IMAGE_SRC`)
- **Override:** When `content.imageSrc` is provided, use it (e.g. ticket-system Types section uses `/images/moduleautoresponder4.svg`)

**Do not:**

- Remove the default constant or the fallback logic `content.imageSrc ?? WHY_CHOOSE_IMAGE_SRC`
- Remove the image or make visibility conditional (image should always render)
- Change the default path for modules that do not set `content.imageSrc` (must remain `atursondrIntro.webp`)

**Allowed:**

- Use `content.imageAlt` for the `alt` attribute
- Let specific module content pass `imageSrc` to override for that page only (e.g. ticket-system)
